    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Moderate to severe atopic dermatitis for at least 5 years

          -  BMI &lt; 30 kg/m2

          -  HbA1c &lt; 42 mmol/mol

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Diabetes

          -  Prediabetes

          -  First-degree relatives with diabetes

          -  Chronic inflammatory diseases other than atopic dermatitis and asthma

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Breast-feeding

          -  Daily intake of medications that are known to influence the glucose metabolism are not
             allowed one month before the study (e.g. asthma medicines and hormonal contraception).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
